---
// A11y legend for the color palette section.
// Extracted to keep the colors page component-based and avoid inline prose clutter.
---

<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center mt-8 mb-1 p-4 bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded text-xs text-gray-700">
  <span class="font-semibold text-gray-1000">A11y check</span>
  <span>
    Each swatch shows its WCAG grade as <em class="not-italic font-semibold">text</em> against
    the surface that fits it — light swatches scored on gray-1000, dark swatches scored on white.
  </span>
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-brand-mono">
    <span
      class="w-4 h-4 rounded inline-flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold text-gray-1000"
      style="background:rgba(0,0,0,.12)"
    >AA</span>
    passes 4.5:1
  </span>
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-brand-mono">
    <span
      class="w-4 h-4 rounded inline-flex items-center justify-center text-[9px] font-bold text-gray-1000 opacity-40"
      style="background:rgba(0,0,0,.12)"
    >·</span>
    fails
  </span>
</div>
